  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5636655/" class="title-link">中东史全貌简要读本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5636655"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/snowbirdflying/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/snowbirdflying/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">snowbird</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-10-31"
      class="main-meta">2012-10-31 11:44:55</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5636655_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  不多的篇幅，一窥中东历史全貌，作为入门读本是首选。废话不多，要点突出，体例有序，值得推荐。翻译上面，中规中矩。对于宗教也能很客观地作出评述，如果对中东有兴趣，建议不妨一读。该书可以作为导读，在此基础上再分阶段深读，很有意思。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
